applicationVersions.description: This subscriber is consuming all material master related change events.
This application is responsible for publishing changes in SAP business object. It can be Boomi Axis, ASAPIO, SAP PI/PO or any app that is capable of publishing changes to Solace as it happens.
This subscriber is consuming all material master change events for PROSYS locality and FERT application for US 60 Sales organization and 902 partner number.
